Class ISOLibrary

  • java.lang.Object
    • alice.tuprolog.Library
      • alice.tuprolog.lib.ISOLibrary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPrimitives, Serializable

    public class ISOLibrary
extends Library
    This class represents a tuProlog library providing most of the built-ins predicates and functors defined by ISO standard. Library/Theory dependency: BasicLibrary
